<!doctype html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>お部屋情報登録</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="main-explanatory-content">
      <div class="new-header">
        <button type="button" class="button-style">airbnb</button>
        <div class="comp-left">
          <span class="h5 text-normal">ステップ２：次に特徴をPR</span>
        </div>
        <div class="comp-right">
          <a>保存して閉じる</a>
        </div>
        <div class="progress" style="height:10px;">
        <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-info" role="progressbar" style="width: 100%" aria-valuenow="100" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="left-explanatory-content">
        <div class="left-content-list">
          <div class="rooms-title">
            <span class="rooms-title-font">説明文を編集する</span>
          </div>
          <%= form_for [@room, @explanatory] do |f| %>
          <div class="rooms-overview">
            <h5>概要</h5>
            <%= f.text_area :overview, {class: 'rooms-explanatory-text_field'}  %>
          </div>

          <div class="rooms-space">
            <h5>お家について（任意）</h5>
            <%= f.text_area :space, {class: 'rooms-explanatory-text_field'}  %>
          </div>

          <div class="rooms-guest_interraction">
            <h5>ゲストが利用可能なエリア（任意）</h5>
            <%= f.text_area :guest_interraction, {class: 'rooms-explanatory-text_field'}  %>
          </div>

          <div class="rooms-guest-access">
            <h5>ゲストとの交流頻度（任意）</h5>
            <%= f.text_area :guest_access, {class: 'rooms-explanatory-text_field'}  %>
          </div>

          <div class="rooms-other_things_to_note">
            <h5>その他の特記事項（任意）</h5>
            <%= f.text_area :other_things_to_note, {class: 'rooms-explanatory-text_field'}  %>
          </div>

          <div class="rooms-title">
            <span class="rooms-title-font">物件に名前をつける</span>
          </div>
            <%= f.text_field :title, {class: 'rooms-location-text_field_lg'}  %>

          <div class="main-panel-action-wrapper">
            <div class="main-panel-half-content clearfix">
              <div class="main-panel-half-spacce">
                <div class="main-panel-half">
                  <%= link_to '← 戻る', new_room_photo_path, class: 'h5 rooms-back-font' %>
                  <%= f.submit '次へ', class: 'rooms-save-btn' %>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>

      <div class="helper-explanatory-content">
        <div class="helper-content-list">
          <div class="card card-style rounded-0" style="width: 20rem;">
            <img class="card-img-top">
            <div class="card-body">
              <span class="fa fa-lightbulb-o fa-3x text-info" aria-hidden="true"></span><br>
              <p class="card-text text-muted">概要説明は宿泊施設の特徴を短くまとめる欄です。ゲストはここで全体像を掴んでから、詳しい説明に読み進みます。</p><br>
              <p class="card-text text-muted">お部屋の説明文で、あらゆるバックグラウンドの人びとを歓迎します、と書いてももちろんOKです</p><br>
              <p class="card-text text-muted">最後にお部屋にふさわしいタイトルをつけましょう！</p><br>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
